- ğŸ“ˆ Brand-wise insights (BoAt, Boult, Noise)  
- ğŸ§© Comparative analysis across features and pricing  
- â­ Customer sentiment and review trend visualization  
- ğŸ“… Automated dashboard refresh using OneDrive-linked data  

